        <p>To add visual interest&comma; I trialed with the brand&apos;s colours from the hills illustrations but found them too dark for Psystem&apos;s desired <span class="bolded">feelings of peace&comma; calmness&comma;</span> and <span class="bolded">security</span>&period;</p>
        <p>Introducing the tertiary colour Ocean Bay provided a brighter hue that</p>
